1. Health
- Show health bars
2. Cannons
- Fire broad side-cannons
- Can fire at any time. Can time to hit multiple targets
3. Oponent Abilities
- If oponent is cornered they might self destruct.
- Running along side a converter enemy type for 3 squares converts your mower to theres.
4. Convert
- If enemy health is low enough you can attempt to convert them like pokemon.
- Are converted enemies removed from play.
- Attempting to convert costs resources. Higher the cost, the more likely to convert (e.g. Ultra ball in pokemon)
5. Economy
- Damaging tiles leads to pay reductions. Should be able to see visual damage at 3-4 stages.
Self destruct completley destroys occupied tile and damages surrounding tiles.
